{"type": "article", "id": 56487, "title": "日本蓝染古布做的手机壳，每一款都独一无二｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-09-17T22:44:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 52802, "name": "Melanie Abrantes"}, {"id": 52803, "name": "Fferrone"}, {"id": 52804, "name": "Malgorzata Bany"}, {"id": 52805, "name": "Simple Union"}, {"id": 52806, "name": "Genevieve Bandrowski"}, {"id": 52807, "name": "Melanie Riccardi"}, {"id": 52808, "name": "Henning Stummel"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 227, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180917200512aCbtQAHLjsuTN3pU.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #337ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #337ab7} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>IPhone Case - Pattern Kofu by Simple Union</h3><p>日本传统的褴褛、古布和蓝染工艺，近年来迎来了一股复兴潮流，为很多时装品牌所追逐，相继运用。香港皮革配件品牌 Simple Union，去年就推出了用日本古布定制的表带以及眼镜皮套等小物。</p><p>最近，赶上苹果刚发布全新 iPhone 系列包括 XS、XS Max 及 XR 三个型号，这次 Simple Union 便决定以古布为主要材质，制作出一系列 iPhone 保护套。</p><p>古布最早出现于日本明治时代，采用了日本传统的染色技术 Katazome，其纺织品织造、制版、印染以至棉花的纺丝全部由工匠手艺一一完成。因此每件产品均属独一无二，其色泽亦会随着时间变化呈现不同效果。售价 480 港币，<a href=\"https://www.simpleunion.tv/product-page-1/iphone-case-pattern-kofu\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180917200647gmG6QzAlfwVuIjtT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180917200647lJNrwQp6IKCES7ik.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180917200648Ay05ieH7NgCj2mf8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666382\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180917200648K8rdNsA7Qu5GLBpc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180917200648Lr19kPG7cm4Ofn2Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809172006493fkuKsWeYqJGOjTM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Nomad by Henning Stummel</h3><p>在今年的伦敦设计节期间，伦敦建筑师 Henning Stummel 将推出皮革和桦木胶合板制成的家具系列 Nomad，包括一个双人沙发，一把扶手椅，和一张咖啡桌。三件单品都是平板式包装家具，设计目的在于尽可能少地浪费材料。</p><p>在 Henning Stummel 看来，组装家具应该是靠生活常识完成，而不是靠繁杂的组装说明。每件家具都由五个部件构成，所有部件都是从一张桦木胶合板上切割下来的。按照 Henning Stummel 的说法，这已经是他为保证完整的框架稳定性所需要的最少件数。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180917200727AWzbj1donwSvYE9O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180917200728HC2aiZmpGNS0hv7t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180917200728g2w0AsZ4EP8qdmML.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809172007307JA2TsMztOHeQVmn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.211083\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809172007294bqWFjyTD2NBuUwx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180917200731nfiH8aV2sMDRxQ9P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180917200730WX2pdykMR06j9eqt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.685279\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/09/16/london-design-festival-nomad-collection-architect-henning-stummels-flat-pack-furniture/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Jesmonite Tables and Lamps by Malgorzata Bany</h3><p>在伦敦 Mayfair 街区的 The New Craftsmen 展厅，家具制造商 Malgorzata Bany 展出了由树脂材料 Jesmonite 制成的家具及家居用品，这是一种耐用的人造材料，由矿物基质和水性丙烯酸树脂制成。</p><p>整个系列包括三张边桌，一张咖啡桌，一张玄关桌和两种不同类型的灯，以及包括碗、盘子和花瓶在内的各种小物件。家具的表面类似于石膏般的光洁度，但比石膏制成的作品更坚固，像石头一样触感冰凉。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809172008096rJb43PVmhwFnfeI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180917200810k2dBVKxyEH1zphRs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809172008080aTHRiK3eOMYX8Lr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180917200811flP2RTWLXMniGy9p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.709391\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180917200811tO2U135xbGZvKgTQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180917200811LmCtTlx14DOyAaSU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180917200812BKZOa54m8xuvTPnh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.thenewcraftsmen.com/makers/malgorzata-bany/\" rel=\"nofollow\">The New Craftsmen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Revolution Glassware by Fferrone</h3><p>捷克品牌 FFERRONE DESIGN 素来以纯手工吹制及捏造玻璃工艺而闻名，比如 Revolution 系列，展现的就是优雅姿态的玻璃器皿。</p><p>它看起来不像是那种高冷的，要被束之高阁的艺术品，日常使用也不会过于高调，长条凹槽的装饰也符合现代主义强调几何线条的脉络，整体呈现流线感。</p><p>Revolution 系列的惊喜藏在杯体中，流动的液体像是悬浮在空中，让酒的色彩与杯体留白的结构产生强烈的视觉冲撞。但仅仅看酒杯的话，它就是个简约纯净的基本几何体。售价 70 美元起，<a href=\"https://fferronedesign.com/collections/revolution-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180917200845VTNCYJgcRx1z48IZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180917200845MuJilh57dApe2Njv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.631875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180917200846WAhPfglEYN3zGR7b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180917200846FSdfUiAXzQmPBj0L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.833125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>The Latest Collection by Melanie Abrantes</h3><p>加州设计品牌 Melanie Abrantes 推出了最新系列的作品，据称其灵感来自荷兰静物画和四季更迭的变化。两位创始人中，Melanie Riccardi 是摄影师，Genevieve Bandrowski 是造型师，她们将这一季的新品融于四个分别描绘春夏秋冬的场景中进行拍摄再创作。</p><p>新系列包括木制烛台、粉红色大理石底座碗，黑色大理石烟灰缸，现代木炭软木花盆和硬木花瓶。售价 55 美元起，<a href=\"http://melanieabrantes.bigcartel.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180917201119bqwOSQINV2meayvG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180917201120ojz7WMu5gmxXkqC9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809172011210aWu54sigSAFkqQ6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180917201121IQ12pYcSA7fqrRyK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809172011227szckrNXBnHT8Adx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180917201119OdxW1LMHTC9XBSfp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}